{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/10.gif?t=1736509932\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Origin</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a plane plunged into the heart of Samomor town, 19 children started disappearing mysteriously. To break the cycle of sorrow, two brave students, you and Jack, embarked on a quest to uncover the root cause.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/01-die.gif?t=1736509932\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Anyone can be eliminated. The story changes as each person disappears</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't murder anyone, or the game will change almost completely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/Overview_Gif.gif?t=1736509932\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Real-time combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you can\u2019t just mash buttons. Every move requires careful planning, but your dog will be by your side, guiding you through every challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/03-Mix.gif?t=1736509932\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Craft and mix your own abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can mix different abilities to create many random variations. With over 40 abilities and 15 weapon skills, master the battles with your own crafted formula.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Other features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A complex story with many choices that can change the game's narrative completely</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Befriend and accompany humorous NPCs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a fully open world with caves, puzzles, treasures, and special challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your character's appearance with 40+ pieces of equipment</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2373890?t=1736509932","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2373890?t=1736509932","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/1b307059aa81a09473041bd67c186ade0bb448ca/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736509932","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/1b307059aa81a09473041bd67c186ade0bb448ca/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736509932","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Unrealistic blood. Suicide. Unrealistic violence. Gore. Body Horror. Uncomfortable choices."},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2491270,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/10.gif?t=1736509932\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Origin</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a plane plunged into the heart of Samomor town, 19 children started disappearing mysteriously. To break the cycle of sorrow, two brave students, you and Jack, embarked on a quest to uncover the root cause.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/01-die.gif?t=1736509932\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Anyone can be eliminated. The story changes as each person disappears</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't murder anyone, or the game will change almost completely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/Overview_Gif.gif?t=1736509932\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Real-time combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you can\u2019t just mash buttons. Every move requires careful planning, but your dog will be by your side, guiding you through every challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/03-Mix.gif?t=1736509932\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Craft and mix your own abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can mix different abilities to create many random variations. With over 40 abilities and 15 weapon skills, master the battles with your own crafted formula.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Other features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A complex story with many choices that can change the game's narrative completely</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Befriend and accompany humorous NPCs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a fully open world with caves, puzzles, treasures, and special challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your character's appearance with 40+ pieces of equipment</p></li></ul>","developers":["Sang Hendrix"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/header.jpg?t=1736509932","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu 18.04 or newer<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i3-2100T or AMD FX-4100<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Intel HD Graphics 300